title: HIgh School Football Player Intercepts Quarterback Who Tries to Spike the Ball
text:
The only time I expected to see a defensive player pick off a quarterback when they spiked the ball would be in Madden . Every now and then, though, high school football always finds a way to make the seemingly impossible possible. Here's Exhibit A.
Cue the collective "WTF?!?"
[via Bleacher Report ]
